dealers butcould possibly affect IBM and Digital Equipment Corp.andP;  It could have a prettybig impact on pricing.&quot;andM;&quot;It's a great victory,&quot; said Barbara Pequignot, federal marketing directorfor Comdisco Inc., Rosemont, Ill.andP;  &quot;It opens up a brand new market for usedcompanies and should mean better prices for the government.&quot;andO;</TEXT></DOC>